M. Antonius de Dominis Archbishop of Spalato, declares the cause of his returne, out of England. Translated out of the Latin copy, printed at Rome this prese[n]t yeare Marcus Antonius de Dominis archiepisc. Spalaten. sui reditus ex Anglia consilium exponit. English De Dominis, Marco Antonio, 1560-1624. Coffin, Edward, 1571-1626.
86 p.
Printed by the English College Press] Permissu superiorum, [Saint-Omer : M.DC.XXIII. [1623]
A translation, by Edward Coffin, of: Marcus Antonius de Dominis archiepisc. Spalaten. sui reditus ex Anglia consilium exponit. Identification of printer from STC. Running title reads: M. Antonius de Dominis his recantation. Reproduction of the original in Emmanuel College (University of Cambridge). Library. Tightly bound; pages 4-5, 34-45, 54-55 from Henry E. Huntington Library and Art Gallery copy filmed at end.
